        "Maintain confidence state in internal isolated context",
        "State includes: layerIdentified (0.0-1.0), stageIdentified (0.0-1.0), rulesAwareness (0.0-1.0), inheritanceResolved (0.0-1.0), requiredContextLoaded (0.0-1.0), overallConfidence (0.0-1.0)",
        "Respond to state request messages with current confidence state",
        "Parse and validate state update messages",
        "Validate confidence scores: must be between 0.0 and 1.0 (inclusive)",
        "Calculate overallConfidence as weighted average: layerIdentified (0.25) + stageIdentified (0.15) + rulesAwareness (0.25) + inheritanceResolved (0.15) + requiredContextLoaded (0.20)",
        "Recalculate overallConfidence whenever any component score changes",
        "Default state: all scores = 0.0",
        "Error handling: If confidence score is outside 0.0-1.0 range, reject update with validation error."
      ],
